HEADWORD: Redeye
<hw>Red"eye`</hw> <pr>(r⟦ecr⟧d"⟦imac⟧`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>The rudd.</def> <sd>(b)</sd>
<def>Same as <er>Redfish</er> <sd>(d)</sd>.</def> <sd>(c)</sd> <def>The
